
  Aurorus    Rock Type Pokémon

  The diamond-shaped crystals 
  on its body expel air as cold 
  as -240 degrees Fahrenheit, surrounding 
  its enemies and encasing them 
  in ice. 
	Evolution Chain
      Amaura ► Aurorus

